title: EYL #203 Keys to Day Trading, Stock Investing, & Marketing with Aristotle Investments
itunes:title: EYL #203 Keys to Day Trading, Stock Investing, & Marketing with Aristotle Investments
description:
In this episode we sat down with online investment sensation Aristotle Investments. He talked about his history in the military and how he became a millionaire before the age of 24.

He explained the difference between swing and day trading and talked about some of the best practices that he uses when trading stocks. #daytrading #investing #stocks 

Link to Aristotle's Mentorship ($1,000 off): http://HoneydripEYL.Com
